Package net.usikkert.kouinject.factory

Contains classes for handling user-created factories.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
FactoryContext Contains details about the requested injection.
FactoryPoint<T> This interface represents a factory point like a method or a field.
FactoryPointHandler Interface for getting meta-data about factory points from beans.
 

Class Summary
AnnotationBasedFactoryPointHandler Implementation of FactoryPointHandler that uses annotations and reflection to scan beans for meta-data about factory points.
FactoryContextImpl A basic implementation of FactoryContext.
FactoryPointMap Map with all the registered factory points and the beans they can create.
FactoryPointMethod<T> An implementation of FactoryPoint for representing factory methods.
 

Package net.usikkert.kouinject.factory Description

Contains classes for handling user-created factories.
